APICoin,is,a,secure,API,service,for,Bitcoin,exchange,and,Bitcoin,information,The,APICoin,BlockExplorer,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,Bitcoin,information,with,other,applications,and,to,create,new,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,Bitcoin,data,by,block,retrieving,block,counts,and,returning,total,Bitcoins